	SPDX-License-Identifier: CC-BY-4.0 WITH Oreo-trademarks

Being under the terms of the Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International
License, as set out in:

	LICENSES/preferred/CC-BY-4.0

EXCEPTION (names, mascot, and royalties)
========================================

Both grants above carry an explicit trademark, naming, and royalty exception:

	LICENSES/exceptions/Oreo-trademarks

The Oreo mascot character, the chest "E-badge", the "Elixpo", "Oreo",
"Oreo Badge", and "OreoOS" names, the elixpo.com and *.elixpo.com identifiers,
and the brand palette are reserved trademarks of the Elixpo project. The
licenses above grant rights to the code and asset files as files. They do NOT
grant rights to the Elixpo or Oreo brand, nor the right to offer a competing
product or hardware device under the Elixpo or Oreo name. This is what protects
the ecosystem's royalties while keeping the code and assets free and open. See
the exception for the full terms (including permitted referential use).

