NOTICE BOARD (per-product reservations)
=======================================

Some Elixpo products ship exclusive artifacts on top of their source - a
published package, a hosted SaaS service, a firmware/OTA release bundle, a
reserved hardware design, a paid tier, and so on. Any such product-specific
reservation is declared in:

	LICENSES/NOTICE   (the notice board)

Where the NOTICE file adds a reservation for an exclusive artifact, that
reservation governs that artifact, in addition to this LICENSE.

